From the School

The story you create for yourself during the next four years could be the most important one you ever write. And what better setting for that story than a comprehensive research university informed by the liberal arts and Catholic intellectual tradition in the exciting, opportunity-rich environment of the nation's capital?

With 12 schools, more than 70 undergraduate programs, and 32 research centers and facilities, CatholicU still maintains the nurturing feel of an undergraduate college. Inspired by our rich 133-year history, CatholicU welcomes undergraduate and graduate students of all faiths from around the globe to study with world-class faculty at the forefront of their fields.

CatholicU combines world-class academics, individualized support, and unsurpassed opportunities for internships to help students maximize their talents, skills, and abilities.
